---
import WatercolorIcon from "./WatercolorIcon.astro";
---

<section id="getting-there" class="py-10 sm:py-12 bg-white scroll-mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-11">
      <p class="font-display italic text-gold text-lg mb-2">Plan your journey</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-wine tracking-tight">Getting There</h2>
      <div class="section-rule mt-5" aria-hidden="true"><span>§</span></div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-charcoal/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Epinac sits in the beautiful Burgundy countryside, roughly halfway between Paris and Lyon.
        Here are your best options for getting to us.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 sm:mb-10">
      <!-- By Air -->
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-5">
          <WatercolorIcon src="/illustrations/wc-plane.jpg" alt="" size="xl" />
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-wine leading-tight">By Air</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-charcoal/70">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Lyon Saint-Exup&eacute;ry (LYS)</strong> &mdash; 2h drive. Best for European and international flights.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Paris CDG / Orly</strong> &mdash; Fly into Paris, then take the TGV to Le Creusot (1h20). We&rsquo;ll arrange a pickup.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Geneva (GVA)</strong> &mdash; 2h drive. Good for transatlantic connections.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Dijon</strong> &mdash; 1h drive. Small regional airport.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- By Train -->
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-5">
          <WatercolorIcon src="/illustrations/wc-train.jpg" alt="" size="xl" />
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-wine leading-tight">By Train</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-charcoal/70">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Le Creusot TGV</strong> &mdash; Just 1h20 from Paris Gare de Lyon. Then a 30-minute drive to Epinac. This is the easiest option from Paris.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Chagny station</strong> &mdash; On the Paris-Lyon main line, 30 minutes&rsquo; drive from the venue.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>Autun station</strong> &mdash; Just 20 minutes from Epinac. Regional connections available.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mt-4">Book trains on <a href="https://www.sncf-connect.com/en-en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-wine">SNCF Connect</a> or <a href="https://www.thetrainline.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-wine">Trainline</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- By Car -->
      <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-5">
          <WatercolorIcon src="/illustrations/wc-car.jpg" alt="" size="xl" />
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-wine leading-tight">By Car</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-charcoal/70">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>From Paris</strong> &mdash; ~3 hours via A6 motorway towards Lyon, exit at Pouilly-en-Auxois or Beaune.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>From Lyon</strong> &mdash; ~2 hours north via A6.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
            <span><strong>From Geneva</strong> &mdash; ~2.5 hours via A40 then A6.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/50 mt-4">Car rentals available at Le Creusot, Lyon, and Paris airports.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Transfers -->
    <div class="bg-wine/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Need a Transfer?</h3>
      <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-6">
        We&rsquo;re coordinating rides between stations/airports and the venue. If you need a
        pickup &mdash; or if you&rsquo;re driving and can offer a spare seat &mdash; please let us
        know via the travel form so we can match everyone up.
      </p>
      <a href="#travel-form" class="inline-block bg-wine hover:bg-wine-dark text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-full transition-colors text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
        Fill Out the Travel Form
      </a>
    </div>

    <div id="see-you" class="mt-10 sm:mt-12 pt-10 sm:pt-12 border-t border-charcoal/10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center px-4 sm:px-6 scroll-mt-16">
      <img
        src="/wedding.jpg"
        alt="Hanna and Jon"
        class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg object-cover aspect-[4/5] sm:aspect-[3/4]"
        width="448"
        height="560"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-wine italic mt-8 sm:mt-10 leading-snug">
        We can&rsquo;t wait to see you there.
      </p>
      <p class="text-charcoal/55 text-sm sm:text-base mt-3">Hanna &amp; Jon</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
